title: Stick Soldiers II PC Game
description:
Stick Soldiers II 1.0.0.1
If you liked Stick Soldiers 1, then you&#039;re going to love this one. Some improvements
 include great mod-ability--you can actually change weapon values, and create new ones, 
and make and edit your own bots. The game also has better graphics; now the camera moves 
with your soldier. Plus, there are cool special effects. The game has tons of mods, maps,
 sounds, weapons, and stuff to download. The only disadvantage is it&#039;s not playable online.
Requirements:
    Windows Me/XP
